<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20201027/c9e57258bfab4375a64e54f3df237093.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>主摄 逆光</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20201027/8c0632058e0645f091e119eb804e2115.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
